# Architecture sync

Before editing module boundaries or adding files under `src/lib/`:

1. Read [docs/architecture.md](docs/architecture.md).

After structural changes (new/moved modules, data flow, CLI flags, exit codes, lifecycle):

1. Update [docs/architecture.md](docs/architecture.md) — module table, diagram, ownership, CLI surface.
2. Update [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) if build commands or layout changed.

Do not merge structural refactors without updating the architecture doc in the same change.
